\SetAPI{J}
\section{ambeth.ioc.objectcollector.active}
\label{configuration:AmbethIocObjectcollectorActive}
\ClearAPI
Switches the object collector/object pool feature (see \nameref{extendable:ICollectableControllerExtendable}) on ("true") or off ("false"). Default is "true".\\

\begin{lstlisting}[style=Props,caption={Usage example for \textit{ambeth.ioc.objectcollector.active}}]

\end{lstlisting}
